     <example>
            <statement>
                <p>Determine if each function represented in a table <em>could</em> could represent a quadratic function.</p>
                    <sidebyside widths="30% 30% 30%" margins="0%">
                            <table>
                                <caption>Function a.</caption>
                                <tabular bottom="minor"  left="minor" top="minor">
                                <col halign="right" right="minor"/>
                                <col halign="right" right="minor"/>
                                <row bottom="medium">
                                    <cell halign="center"><m>x</m></cell>
                                    <cell halign="center"><m>f(x)</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>-3</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>11</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>-2</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>7</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>-1</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>3</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>0</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-1</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>1</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-5</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>2</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-9</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>3</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-13</m></cell>
                                </row>
                            </tabular></table>
                        
                            <table>
                            <caption>Function b.</caption>
                            <tabular valign="top" bottom="minor"  left="minor" top="minor">
                                <col halign="right" right="minor"/>
                                <col halign="right" right="minor"/>
                                <row bottom="medium">
                                    <cell halign="center"><m>x</m></cell>
                                    <cell halign="center"><m>g(x)</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>-3</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-9</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>-2</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-4</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>-1</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-1</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>0</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>0</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>1</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-1</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>2</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-4</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>3</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-9</m></cell>
                                </row>
                            </tabular>
                            </table>
                        
                            <table>
                            <caption>Function c.</caption>
                            <tabular valign="top" bottom="minor"  left="minor" top="minor">
                                <col halign="right" right="minor"/>
                                <col halign="right" right="minor"/>
                                <row bottom="medium">
                                    <cell halign="center"><m>x</m></cell>
                                    <cell halign="center"><m>p(x)</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>-3</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-8</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>-2</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>4</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>-1</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-7</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>0</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>5</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>1</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-6</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>2</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>6</m></cell>
                                </row>
                                <row>
                                    <cell><m>3</m></cell>
                                    <cell><m>-5</m></cell>
                                </row>
                            </tabular>
                            </table>
                        </sidebyside>
            </statement>
            <solution>
                <p>
                    <ol label="a.">
                        <li><p>The difference between each output for consecutive inputs is constant, so it's possible that this function is a linear function. It is therefore not possible that it is a quadratic function.</p></li>
                        <li><p>This pattern looks to follow the pattern of <m>-x^2</m>, so it is possible that it is a quadratic function.</p></li>
                        <li><p>This function changes from increasing to decreasing (and visa versa) repeatedly, so it is not possible that it is a quadratic function.</p></li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
            </solution>
